===Cardinal number===
'''forty'''

# The cardinal number occurring after thirty-nine and before forty-one, represented in Roman numerals as [[XL]] and in Arabic numerals as 40.  Ordinal: [[fortieth]].
*[[w:Arabic numerals|Arabic numerals]]: 40
*[[w:Roman numerals|Roman numerals]]: XL
**Last: [[thirty]] (30), [[thirty-nine]] (39)
**Next: [[forty-one]] (41), [[fifty]] (50)

